snippet: Rory McIlroy matched the low round of the day with a five-under-par 67 to move three shots off the lead at the Texas Open in San Antonio.
abstract: Rory McIlroy moves within three shots of Texas Open second-round leader Billy Horschel.
lead_paragraph: Rory McIlroy matched the low round of the day with a five-under-par 67 to move three shots off the lead at the Texas Open in San Antonio.
